article.description: — KC Ndefo posted 16 points, seven rebounds and five blocks as St. Peter's got past Fairfield 70-59 on Friday night.
article.headline: Ndefo scores 16 to carry St. Peter's over Fairfield 70-59
article.linkText: Ndefo scores 16 to carry St. Peter's over Fairfield 70-59
article.story: BRIDGEPORT, Conn. -- — KC Ndefo posted 16 points, seven rebounds and five blocks as St. Peter's got past Fairfield 70-59 on Friday night. Matthew Lee had 11 points for St. Peter's (12-10, 10-5 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Supreme Cook had 12 points and seven rebounds for the Stags (12-15, 6-10). Caleb Green added 11 points. Taj Benning had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
